lyTime":"2017-08-06T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"睇你想玩市外定內<br />\n外就平溪線 即係九十分果面 或者再遠去埋基隆果面<br />\n內就夜市簡出名果幾個去 想睇文物文化野就中正紀念堂 故宮果啲 得意文青野就華山/松山文創 四四南村 行街買野就信義區市政府西門町 市內風景就貓空象山<br />\n野食就唔推介 自己搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tw你去淡水就試下阿給 玩下電動車咁 同埋去得淡水就順路去埋士林夜市 都係果面"},{"pid":"d3236423c2722970ae4a622a2eb612be99893c23","tid":349371,"uid":49250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"真心 覺得無野係必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271b4f4e9b1dd758c587949c7b02381e5009a671","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb307bcc01bf5a0894ffc0cc61b9ef3b88905ab","tid":349371,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心 覺得無野係必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港又有咩係必去 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5619ba70e381eac14dbb84828d80aeafef1ebaa","tid":349371,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去旅行 因為熱 所以唔出外? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2afb53ee7e0125e56a25a21b7191c73ba89bee","tid":349371,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟九份十分值唔值得去？<br />\n因為係自己一個去　唔會去放天燈<br />\n有乜地方係真係好靚 可以周圍HEA 行成日<br />\n會去淡水<br />\n唔該各位巴絲</blockquo