,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟九份十分值唔值得去？<br />\n因為係自己一個去　唔會去放天燈<br />\n有乜地方係真係好靚 可以周圍HEA 行成日<br />\n會去淡水<br />\n唔該各位巴絲</blockquote><br />\n第一次去咪當見識下囉<br />\n九份勁商業化好逼人，類似去咗赤柱市集，去一次就夠<br />\n十分感覺舒服好多，又可以行下火車軌幾得意，自己唔放天燈咪睇人玩，都幾過癮"},{"pid":"f6d86cbb8f04a9059bf3be4181204924ebe69d62","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去旅行 因為熱 所以唔出外? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，有咩問題？"},{"pid":"d736436025ea12df52b373e0525243ffc3ed9975","tid":349371,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咁你唔好留喺香港租酒店 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑,  咁不如去返廣東省算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3cf4dacbff636d58e45fc3a2cadeac6cc30575","tid":349371,"uid":74255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:38:03.000Z","msg":"九份十分基隆<br />\n 西門町 台北車站地下街<br />\n淡水 漁人碼頭 士林夜市<br />\n鼎泰豐 <br />\n個人去左十次台北 岩唔岩行見人見志 個人去親都必去"},{"pid":"afc8084b234b8f6133fe2e751f6cfecf9b29712b","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咁你唔好留喺香港租酒店 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑,  咁不如去返廣東省算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸？不了。"},{"pid":"6f05702d3c969df011ea1d7ed1fd670517b2535f","tid":349371,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咁你唔好留喺香港租酒店 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑,  咁不如去返廣東省算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸？不了。</blockquote><br />\n唔出門 去廣州同去台灣無咩分別"},{"pid":"5771f753119da209432d1c3bafc91f7575619e15","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咁你唔好留喺香港租酒店 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑,  咁不如去返廣東省算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸？不了。</blockquote><br />\n唔出門 去廣州同去台灣無咩分別</blockquote><br />\n當然唔係唔出門既<br />\n落下夜市買下野食買下衫褲咁囉<br />\n<br />\n果日去淡水，行十分鐘成件衫都濕哂，好唔舒服<br />\n咩心情都冇撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fd16e746e0b513c4a2fd2e914d2276cdc5dded","tid":349371,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55d0ffc31c7942db4e0bcf22171ccc95405a0a0","tid":349371,"uid":44487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"萬里橋頭滑翔傘"},{"pid":"c6775206be450528a27cfc5873627890c861c7eb","tid":349371,"uid":2377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去旅行 因為熱 所以唔出外? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n咁你去南北極住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b525e2090e8c23ade81d02d2b5b55f4e8cb633","tid":349371,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"上面好笑<br />\n台北e個時候唔打風就又熱又焗<br />\n去ed地方出街唔帶多件衫換咪自己抵死<br />\n去旅行行酒店附近不如留係屋企打飛機，肚餓想行街時落屋企樓下附近行都一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ba0547acfb37c0d2f4e6996293233ccce5f7c7","tid":349371,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍山寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374aa9fdfc043da94916602e3b30b2bef39faba9","tid":349371,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過新北投浸温泉</blockquote><br />\n三二唔錯"},{"pid":"ac71420ec084947b8977f502a4103a2eb1d9f12b","tid":349371,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"一定要食太和殿麻辣火鍋<br />\n鴨血豆腐任添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ad14e047ad14aa3ed185489ff5014d089f3672","tid":349371,"uid":35653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係台北夏季無落雨咪算你好彩囉 傻9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2dda1339d6abd5ece642a511cdb1b88e92813","tid":349371,"uid":132684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"陽明山"},{"pid":"87ab5b29d5fdb2f8aee7e39496e921fd2f83d01c","tid":349371,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"上引水產必去。<br />\n無去過既話唔好話人知你去過台北。"},{"pid":"4b02569813b8cbaa5f8851843265a860a328b3f4","tid":349371,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面好笑<br />\n台北e個時候唔打風就又熱又焗<br />\n去ed地方出街唔帶多件衫換咪自己抵死<br />\n去旅行行酒店附近不如留係屋企打飛機，肚餓想行街時落屋企樓下附近行都一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實stay酒店真係無乜問題 特別如果間酒店正<br />\n去旅行hea下 想食先搭的士出去食野<br />\n唔係一定要行街去景點"},{"pid":"9913c7149284232dbb9dccc0b6073a4e259413ee","tid":349371,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟九份十分值唔值得去？<br />\n因為係自己一個去　唔會去放天燈<br />\n有乜地方係真係好靚 可以周圍HEA 行成日<br />\n會去淡水<br />\n唔該各位巴絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淡水我覺得伏<br />\n日落麻麻❨可能唔好彩❩<br />\n無咩睇 係買下手信食下野"},{"pid":"99d29e21aa1211c1b8fd68a3104b1fc3fc50b838","tid":349371,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"去過一次都無咩特別話想去多次,<br />\n因為成日落雨太撚煩"},{"pid":"f3899fd9920a1e68f6e4131e6cb5f0af64a61401","tid":349371,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟九份十分值唔值得去？<br />\n因為係自己一個去　唔會去放天燈<br />\n有乜地方係真係好靚 可以周圍HEA 行成日<br />\n會去淡水<br />\n唔該各位巴絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淡水我覺得伏<br />\n日落麻麻❨可能唔好彩❩<br />\n無咩睇 係買下手信食下野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n必去就唔敢講 個人覺得比較好玩<br />\n九份-&gt;十分❨幾個站❩-&gt;基隆夜市<br />\n都玩足一日<br />\n野柳 金山 富漁港 北海岸一日遊 都幾正<br />\n仲有新北投温泉"},{"pid":"cd0754935523225f215cd29e2fafe7b5dd7d6d1d","tid":349371,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"去誠品瘋狂打書釘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848ae2de920dc368c4aadaf4bfbd6fd7d24f571f","tid":349371,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"ONE PIECE CAFE"},{"pid":"f60fce1c45bcceb71681a264370038b41da49e65","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去旅行 因為熱 所以唔出外? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n咁你去南北極住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想"},{"pid":"043c4cee5dfd7a9e401450642fb4f1e065cf83dd","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面好笑<br />\n台北e個時候唔打風就又熱又焗<br />\n去ed地方出街唔帶多件衫換咪自己抵死<br />\n去旅行行酒店附近不如留係屋企打飛機，肚餓想行街時落屋企樓下附近行都一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你平時趕開景點？<br />\n係咪覺得4日3夜要去勻10個8個景點先夠哂抵返張機票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4667070d1eb7d2523347888a6b2ca43b2a855c7","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完台北4日，覺得冇乜必要唔好出旅館<br />\n出面熱撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係台北夏季無落雨咪算你好彩囉 傻9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係架，我坐捷運去淡水果日<br />\n一出門口就落大雨（我住大同區）<br />\n去到淡水曬撚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ab52c7cdbe4bf61f50c5b848cda858202a6a7e","tid":349371,"uid":130616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"上陽明山"},{"pid":"b493e052e387e08e3d82557d4e1f57318d41c84f","tid":349371,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"人在高雄 日日暴曬<br />\n返去成身汗味<br />\n即刻除衫沖個靚涼<br />\n買定凍茶係hostel雪櫃 攤係床飲<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8f7627f73a76d8176cb8d3e28d24d16b2b2c55","tid":349371,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"西門町  美觀園食魚生"},{"pid":"53202f7e804b44b10270dd631e9cab30410ac67b","tid":349371,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人在高雄 日日暴曬<br />\n返去成身汗味<br />\n即刻除衫沖個靚涼<br />\n買定凍茶係hostel雪櫃 攤係床飲<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我有諗過8月中再飛多轉3日2夜高雄<br />\n但一諗到咁鳩熱，真係不了<br />\n<br />\n11月再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}